    "media": {
      "document": "# Media Plan — Luminary Health, Q3 2025 (NA)\n\n## Scope\n\nAdvertiser: Luminary Health (LMH). Markets: US (EN + ES). Flight: Jul 1 – Sep 30, 2025.\nObjective: prospecting + retargeting for appointment bookings.\n\n## Media Partners & Connectors\n\n- Meta (Facebook + Instagram) — connector: Direct Publisher (walled garden). Click tracking: On.\n- DV360 — connector: Google DV360 (served). Click tracking: On.\n- Yahoo DSP — connector: Yahoo DSP 3PAS (served). Click tracking: On.\n\n## Partner Campaigns & Ad Groups (external)\n\n- Meta campaign \"LMH_Q325_Prospecting_Meta\" with ad groups: AG_Meta_EN_HighIntent, AG_Meta_EN_Broad, AG_Meta_ES_HighIntent.\n- DV360 campaign \"LMH_Q325_Retarget_DV360\" with ad group: AG_DV360_Retarget.\n- Yahoo campaign \"LMH_Q325_Prospecting_Yahoo\" with ad group: AG_Yahoo_Prosp.\n\n## Placement Groups\n\n- PS_LMH_Q325_Meta_EN_Prosp — seat: Luminary Health, advertiser: LMH, binds to Meta campaign LMH_Q325_Prospecting_Meta.\n- PS_LMH_Q325_DV360_Retarget — seat: Luminary Health, advertiser: LMH, binds to DV360 campaign LMH_Q325_Retarget_DV360.\n- PS_LMH_Q325_Yahoo_Prosp — seat: Luminary Health, advertiser: LMH, binds to Yahoo campaign LMH_Q325_Prospecting_Yahoo.\n\n## Placements\n\nWalled garden (Meta, 1:1 placement ↔ ad group):\n\n- P_LMH_FB_EN_HighIntent → AG_Meta_EN_HighIntent. Feed, Adaptive. Under PS_LMH_Q325_Meta_EN_Prosp.\n- P_LMH_FB_EN_Broad → AG_Meta_EN_Broad. Feed, Adaptive. Under PS_LMH_Q325_Meta_EN_Prosp.\n- P_LMH_FB_ES_HighIntent → AG_Meta_ES_HighIntent. Feed, Adaptive. Under PS_LMH_Q325_Meta_EN_Prosp.\n\nServed (DV360, many placements : 1 ad group):\n\n- P_LMH_DV360_Ret_300x250 → AG_DV360_Retarget. Standard Display (HTML), 300x250. Under PS_LMH_Q325_DV360_Retarget.\n- P_LMH_DV360_Ret_728x90 → AG_DV360_Retarget. Standard Display (HTML), 728x90. Under PS_LMH_Q325_DV360_Retarget.\n- P_LMH_DV360_Ret_160x600 → AG_DV360_Retarget. Standard Display (HTML), 160x600. Under PS_LMH_Q325_DV360_Retarget.\n\nServed (Yahoo):\n\n- P_LMH_Yahoo_Prosp_300x250 → AG_Yahoo_Prosp. Standard Display (HTML), 300x250. Under PS_LMH_Q325_Yahoo_Prosp.\n\n## Experience Groups & Flights\n\n- EG_LMH_EN_HighIntent (Adaptive, LIVE) on P_LMH_FB_EN_HighIntent and the DV360 retarget placements.\n- EG_LMH_EN_Broad (Adaptive) on P_LMH_FB_EN_Broad.\n- EG_LMH_ES_HighIntent (Adaptive) on P_LMH_FB_ES_HighIntent and P_LMH_Yahoo_Prosp_300x250.\n\n## Creatives\n\n- crv_LMH_Hero_EN_Image (Adaptive, 300x250 / 1200x628) under EG_LMH_EN_HighIntent and EG_LMH_EN_Broad.\n- crv_LMH_Hero_EN_Video (Adaptive, 1080x1080) under EG_LMH_EN_HighIntent.\n- crv_LMH_Hero_ES_Image (Adaptive, 300x250) under EG_LMH_ES_HighIntent.\n\n## Landing Page Groups & Pages\n\n- LPS_LMH_US_EN_Q3 (scope: US English; EG_LMH_EN_HighIntent, EG_LMH_EN_Broad).\n- LPS_LMH_US_ES_Q3 (scope: US Spanish; EG_LMH_ES_HighIntent).\n\n## Pixels\n\n- PIX_Conv_Appointment — conversion pixel, targets creative crv_LMH_Hero_EN_Image.\n- PIX_Conv_AccountCreated — conversion pixel, targets placement P_LMH_DV360_Ret_300x250.\n",
      "model": {
